No. 09-10028. Winford Kent Bishop, Petitioner v. Departmental Disciplinary Committee for the First Judicial Department. 560 U.S. 937, 130 S. Ct. 3361,

176 L. Ed. 2d 1243,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 4488. June 1, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Appellate Division, Supreme Court of New York, First Judicial Department, dismissed. See Rule 39.8.

Same case below, 54 App. Div. 3d 1, 863 N.Y.S.2d 1.
